data.description:
Single Family Home for rent or Sale!
Stunning 3bd, 3ba, plus bonus room with attached private full bath with stand-up shower and corner Jacuzzi tub. Newly updated large pantry and plenty of counter space in the kitchen with newly installed over-the-stove microwave and fridge/freezer. Large laundry room with newly installed countertop for folding and new cupboards along with storage cabinet.New Hot water heater and pressure tank. The basement has a working wood stove to reduce the electric bill in the winter months and a woodshed outside for plenty of firewood storage to keep it nice and dry. Large finished shed that can easily become a home office with loft for plenty of outside storage. Gravel driveway, large yard, and deck for entertainment year-round with parking space underneath.

All utilities will be paid by the renter. Water is on a well. smoking is not permitted in the home. Pet Deposit of $150 per pet is not refundable.
